text:
Hi guys,

I tried to run the app from following link <https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric/blob/master/docs/gettingstarted.md>. I could successfully complete all the steps, 
When I tried to run different chaincode using same setup. only thing I changed was I included my chaincode in the folder /hackfest/src/github.com/example_cc and I changed the ./src/github.com/example_cc/example_cc.go:/opt/gopath/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric/examples/example_cc.go TO
./src/github.com/example_cc/mychaincodename.go:/opt/gopath/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric/examples/mychaincodename.go

in yml file under cli

when I try to deploy I get following error

<@U3YHGBE01> You need to change the chaincode name as well , please consider changing this value `<https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric-sdk-node/blob/master/examples/balance-transfer/config.json#L3>`
There will be an image already got created with that name.
